# Sanctioned scratch location for bench fixtures.
#
# Harnesses that need to seed a sample ledger on disk write it HERE (or to a
# scratch tmpdir) — NEVER to the repo-root .sirius/, which the core agent owns.
# The in-memory FixtureLedger model (bench/lib/ledger.ts) covers current needs,
# so this directory is usually empty; it exists so on-disk fixtures have a home.
